summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2890, for the improvement of 35th Avenue South from King Street to a point ninety feet north of Jackson Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading, construction of gutters together with concrete walks, under Ordinance No. 35088 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
